### Listar empleados
GET http://localhost:8002/empleados
Authorization: Bearer {token}

### Buscar por área
GET http://localhost:8002/empleados?area=Tecnologia
Authorization: Bearer {token}

### Buscar por estado
GET http://localhost:8002/empleados?estado=activo
Authorization: Bearer {token}

### Buscar por documento
GET http://localhost:8002/empleados?documento=1000123456
Authorization: Bearer {token}

### Crear empleado
POST http://localhost:8002/empleados
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {token}

{
    "nombres": "Juan",
    "apellidos": "Perez",
    "documento": "1000999888",
    "correo": "juan@empresa.com",
    "telefono": "3001112233",
    "cargo": "Desarrollador",
    "area": "Tecnologia",
    "fecha_ingreso": "2026-06-11"
}

### Editar empleado
PUT http://localhost:8002/empleados/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {token}

{
    "cargo": "Desarrollador Senior",
    "area": "Tecnologia"
}

### Cambiar estado
PATCH http://localhost:8002/empleados/1/estado
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {token}

{
    "estado": "inactivo"
}